Look at this place.

37:56.310 --> 37:57.710
It's pretty great.

37:58.190 --> 37:59.510
It's amazing.

38:00.270 --> 38:05.710
I got a job, a great place, great friends.

38:11.590 --> 38:13.870
Come on, come on, come on, howl with me.

38:16.350 --> 38:17.230
Come on.

38:19.950 --> 38:21.470
Dude, that was terrible.

38:21.470 --> 38:23.110
What? I'm not one for the howling.

38:23.110 --> 38:24.110
Oh, no?

38:24.110 --> 38:26.190
You just need to be woken up.

38:32.430 --> 38:36.510
Hey, you know, when I'm with you I feel like I can do anything.

38:36.510 --> 38:37.790
And...

38:38.670 --> 38:41.070
I've never felt that way before.

38:43.150 --> 38:44.510
That's sweet.

38:44.510 --> 38:49.670
You know, we're not so different, you and me.

38:49.670 --> 38:52.470
Hey, you know, I think maybe it's time...

38:52.470 --> 38:54.750
Wait, wait, wait.
Where you going?

38:55.270 --> 38:57.190
- Trey, what are you..?
- Come on, come on.

38:57.510 --> 38:59.670
I've seen the way you look at me.

39:00.470 --> 39:03.070
You know, no one's ever been this nice to me.

39:03.070 --> 39:04.670
Yeah, because you're Ryan's brother.

39:04.670 --> 39:06.430
No, it's more than that, and you know it.

39:06.430 --> 39:09.150
And I get it.
You don't want to hurt him.

39:09.150 --> 39:11.110
But he doesn't have to know.

39:11.110 --> 39:13.670
No, Trey.
No. No way. Okay?

39:13.670 --> 39:14.830
Never. What?

39:14.830 --> 39:16.110
What, wait, wait, wait.

39:16.110 --> 39:19.190
- What, I'm not good enough?
- No, look, I don't mean it like that.

39:19.190 --> 39:20.350
- Okay, just let go.
- Come on, come on.

39:20.350 --> 39:23.870
Look, Ryan gets all the good life, huh? Right?

39:25.510 --> 39:26.950
Get off of me.

39:27.670 --> 39:30.510
Come on.
No one needs to know.

39:30.870 --> 39:32.870
Get off me!
Off of me...

39:32.870 --> 39:36.110
Please. Help.

40:01.590 --> 40:04.430
Dude, look what you've done!

40:11.470 --> 40:14.510
I guess those guys really do believe in an eye for an eye.

40:15.550 --> 40:17.590
- Hungry?
- I'll pass.

40:18.270 --> 40:20.190
It's too bad we can't tell anyone what happened.

40:20.190 --> 40:22.430
No one would believe us anyway.

40:22.430 --> 40:25.190
Yeah, it's probably best I don't tell Summer.

40:25.190 --> 40:27.710
Yeah, you know what, man?
I'm going to call Marissa.

40:27.710 --> 40:29.110
Check in, see how she and Trey are doing.

40:29.110 --> 40:29.790
All right.

40:29.790 --> 40:32.390
I'm going to go back to the room and...lick myself clean.

40:32.390 --> 40:34.310
Night.

